Mark Price is a veteran iOS & Android developer having published over 58 mobile apps to-date. He also is a long time game developer and worked on Call of Duty Ghosts in addition to many other mobile games. In addition to professional programming, Mark is an accomplished teacher of technology, having taught at a coding bootcamp and is now teaching full time as an online instructor with multiple successful iOS development courses. When Mark isn't coding or teaching, he is spending time with his wife and children.
